# Git Commit / PR Rule (Rebase Only)

為了避免 PR 出現 merge commit，分支同步 `integration`（目前對應 `develop`）時，統一使用 `rebase`，禁止使用 `merge`。

## 禁止指令（會產生 merge commit）

- `git merge origin/develop`
- `git pull origin develop`

## 正確流程（rebase）

1. `git fetch origin`
2. `git rebase origin/develop`
3. `git push --force-with-lease`

## 建議本機 Git 設定

1. `git config --global pull.rebase true`
2. `git config --global rebase.autoStash true`
3. `git config --global pull.ff only`

## Branch Naming Convention

- Personal branches: `{name}/{purpose}` (e.g., `brandon/dev`, `jacky/feature`)
- Do NOT use department-reserved prefixes: `feature/xxx`, `main/xxx`
- Department branches: `production`, `rc`, `develop`, `hotfix`

## Commit Message Convention

Format: `<type>[<optional scope>]: <description>`

- `scope` is usually the ticket number (Jira or ClickUp), e.g., `fix[AND-333]: implement something.`
- Message body must be in English.
- Common types: `feat`, `fix`, `chore`, `refactor`, `test`, `docs`
